sect2.para:
The &man.gzip.1; utility has been
	updated to add -l support for &man.xz.1;
	files.

The &man.newfs.8; and &man.tunefs.8;
	utilities have been updated to allow underscores in label
	names.

The &man.newfs.8; and &man.tunefs.8;
	utilities have been updated to allow dashes in label
	names.

The &man.file.1; utility has been
	updated to fix incorrect date reporting for &man.dump.8;
	files.

Warnings for features deprecated in
	future releases will now be printed on all &os;
	versions.
